---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Go-Live Readiness — SPA earn-defi.com"
  description="What the code has proven vs what only the owner can do. Governance + money-path defenses fire (reproducible); the remaining blockers are custody, audit, legal and the 30-day evidenced track — owner-only and time-gated."
  canonical="https://earn-defi.com/readiness"
>
  <main class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <section class="pt-16 pb-8">
      <p class="text-xs text-accent-400 font-mono uppercase tracking-widest mb-3" data-ru="Готовность к go-live">Go-Live Readiness</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4 leading-tight" data-ru="Что доказал код против того, что может только владелец">What the code has proven vs what only the owner can do</h1>
      <p class="text-white/60 leading-relaxed" data-ru="Честная поверхность готовности. Защиты доказуемо срабатывают (воспроизводимо, детерминированно). Оставшиеся блокеры — кастоди, аудит, легал и 30 evidenced-дней трека — owner-only и time-gated. Ничто здесь не двигает капитал.">
        An honest readiness surface. The safety defenses are proven to fire — reproducibly, deterministically, through the same governance code the daily cycle uses. The remaining blockers — custody, audit, legal, and 30 evidenced track-days — are owner-only and time-gated. Nothing here moves capital.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="py-6 border-t border-border">
      <p class="text-xs text-white/50 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono mb-4" data-ru="Живой статус">Live status</p>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4" id="rdy-cards">
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-bg-surface border border-border p-5">
          <p class="text-xs text-accent-400 font-mono uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Governance defenses</p>
          <p class="text-2xl font-mono font-bold text-white"><span id="rdy-def">—</span></p>
          <p class="text-xs text-white/55 mt-1" data-ru="срабатывают на стрессе (SOFT −5% / HARD −10%)">fire on stress (SOFT −5% / HARD −10%)</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-bg-surface border border-border p-5">
          <p class="text-xs text-accent-400 font-mono uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Go-live gate</p>
          <p class="text-2xl font-mono font-bold text-white"><span id="rdy-gate">—</span></p>
          <p class="text-xs text-white/55 mt-1"><span id="rdy-days">—</span> <span data-ru="evidenced-дней трека">evidenced track-days</span></p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-bg-surface border border-border p-5">
          <p class="text-xs text-accent-400 font-mono uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Target</p>
          <p class="text-2xl font-mono font-bold text-white"><span id="rdy-target">—</span></p>
          <p class="text-xs text-white/55 mt-1" data-ru="время, не код">time-gated, not code</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-xl bg-bg-surface border border-border p-5">
          <p class="text-xs text-accent-400 font-mono uppercase tracking-wider mb-2" data-ru="Серия READY-дней">Ready streak</p>
          <p class="text-2xl font-mono font-bold text-white"><span id="rdy-streak">—</span></p>
          <p class="text-xs text-white/55 mt-1" data-ru="подряд READY-дней (нужно 7 устойчивых)">consecutive READY days (7 sustained wanted)</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-6 border-t border-border">
      <p class="text-xs text-white/50 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono mb-4" data-ru="Блокеры только для владельца (код не может их закрыть)">Owner-only blockers (code cannot satisfy these)<span id="rdy-blockers-count" class="text-white/35 normal-case"></span></p>
      <ul class="space-y-2" id="rdy-blockers">
        <li class="text-sm text-white/50">—</li>
      </ul>
    </section>

    <section class="py-6 border-t border-border">
      <p class="text-xs text-accent-400 uppercase tracking-wider font-mono mb-4" data-ru="Проверьте сами">Reproduce it yourself</p>
      <pre class="text-xs font-mono text-white/70 overflow-x-auto rounded-lg bg-bg-surface border border-border p-4">python3 scripts/verify_spa.py data/                    # proof chain intact
python3 scripts/defenses_exercised_report.py          # 11/11 defenses fire
python3 -m spa_core.paper_trading.pre_cutover_gate     # 16/16 money-path defenses (inert)
python3 scripts/kill_switch_drill.py                   # emergency-stop latency drill (dated evidence)</pre>
      <p class="text-xs text-white/60 mt-3 font-mono" data-ru="Дрилл аварийного стопа (kill-switch):">
        Emergency-stop (kill-switch) drill: <span id="rdy-ksd" class="text-white/80">—</span>
      </p>
      <p class="text-xs text-white/50 mt-3" id="rdy-honest" data-ru="Код доказывает защиты; кастоди / аудит / легал / 30-дневный трек — owner-only и time-gated.">The code proves the defenses fire; custody / audit / legal / the 30-day evidenced track are owner-only and time-gated.</p>
    </section>
  </main>

  <script is:inline>
    (function(){
      var API = (location.hostname==='localhost'||location.hostname==='127.0.0.1') ? 'http://localhost:8765' : 'https://api.earn-defi.com';
      function set(id, v){ var el=document.getElementById(id); if(el) el.textContent=v; }
      fetch(API+'/api/readiness').then(function(r){return r.json();}).then(function(d){
        var g=d.governance_defenses||{}, gl=d.go_live_gate||{};
        if(g.fired!=null) set('rdy-def', g.fired+'/'+g.total+(g.all_fired?' ✓':''));
        if(gl.passed!=null) set('rdy-gate', gl.passed+'/'+gl.total);
        if(gl.evidenced_days!=null) set('rdy-days', gl.evidenced_days+'/'+(gl.days_needed||30));
        if(gl.target_date) set('rdy-target', gl.target_date);
        if(gl.consecutive_ready_days!=null) set('rdy-streak', gl.consecutive_ready_days+'/'+(gl.consecutive_ready_days_needed||7));
        var k=d.kill_switch_drill||{};
        if(k.latency_ms!=null){ var dt=(k.last_drill_at||'').slice(0,10); set('rdy-ksd', (k.verdict||'')+' · '+k.latency_ms+'ms / '+(k.latency_limit_ms||1000)+'ms budget'+(dt?(' · '+dt):'')); }
        var ul=document.getElementById('rdy-blockers');
        // Q1-9: prefer the richer per-gate tracker (status open/in_progress/satisfied);
        // fall back to the flat list for older API responses.
        var ob=d.owner_blockers, gates=(ob&&Array.isArray(ob.gates))?ob.gates:d.owner_only_blockers;
        if(ul && Array.isArray(gates)){
          ul.innerHTML='';
          var badge={open:['open','text-warn bg-warn/10 border-warn/30'],
                     in_progress:['in progress','text-accent-400 bg-accent-400/10 border-accent-400/30'],
                     satisfied:['satisfied','text-ok bg-ok/10 border-ok/30']};
          gates.forEach(function(b){
            var st=b.status||'', bd=badge[st]||['','text-white/40 border-white/15'];
            var li=document.createElement('li');
            li.className='text-sm text-white/55 flex gap-2 items-start';
            var pill= st ? ('<span class="text-[10px] font-mono px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded border '+bd[1]+' flex-shrink-0">'+bd[0]+'</span>') : '<span class="text-warn flex-shrink-0">•</span>';
            var detail = b.detail ? (' <span class="text-white/40">— '+b.detail+'</span>') : '';
            li.innerHTML=pill+'<span><b class="text-white/75">'+b.id+'</b> — '+b.what+detail+'</span>';
            ul.appendChild(li);
          });
          var ts=document.getElementById('rdy-blockers-count');
          if(ts && ob && ob.open_count!=null) ts.textContent=' — '+ob.open_count+'/'+ob.total+' still open';
        }
        if(d.honest) set('rdy-honest', d.honest);
      }).catch(function(){ set('rdy-def','unavailable'); });
    })();
  </script>
</Layout>
